  "text": "Clomiphene citrate acts by binding to estrogen receptor (ER), and exerts a weak estrogenic effect while blocking endogenous estrogen [CITATION_1] . Potential mechanism of action of clomiphene citrate may be through estrogenic transcriptional activity, and these influences are possibly dependent on its dose, endogenous tissue metabolism and the hormonal environment [CITATION_2] .",
